OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FChannel 4 has said it is "deeply
OL,8,Fsorry" for the distress caused to
OL,9,Fparticipants on Married At First Sight
OL,10,FUK following allegations of rape and
OL,11,Fsexual assault made by former
OL,12,Fcontestants.
OL,14,FChief executive Priya Dogra said an
OL,15,Fexternal review was under way after
OL,16,Ftwo women told the BBC's Panorama
OL,17,Fprogramme they were allegedly raped by
OL,18,Ftheir on-screen partners during
OL,19,Ffilming.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
