CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FA third accused her on-screen partner
OL,8,Fof sexual misconduct.
OL,10,FThe women claimed the incidents took
OL,11,Fplace while appearing on the reality
OL,12,Fdating series. All three men deny the
OL,13,Fallegations.
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, senior figures at
OL,16,FChannel 4, including chief executive
OL,17,FPriya Dogra, spoke at a briefing for
OL,18,Fthe broadcaster's annual report at an
OL,19,Fevent in London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FSpeaking to reporters on Wednesday, Ms
OL,8,FDogra: "While I attempt to do my best
OL,9,Fto answer questions, I'll ask their
OL,10,Fforbearance because there are
OL,11,Flimitations on what I can say before
OL,12,Fthis review is complete late in the
OL,13,Fsummer.
OL,26,@pD@HOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,F"That said I have watched the
OL,8,F(Panorama) programme and heard the
OL,9,Fwomen's accounts, which are very
OL,10,Ftroubling. Their distress is clear,
OL,11,Fand for that I am, of course, deeply
OL,12,Fsorry. Welfare across all our
OL,13,Fprogrammes is hugely important to us,
OL,14,Fand is a primary concern.
OL,16,F"However, I'm sure you'll appreciate
OL,17,Fthat Channel 4 cannot investigate the
OL,18,Fspecific allegations against the men,
OL,19,Fwhich they have denied, nor can I
OL,20,Fcomment on them in any way.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,F"We are a broadcaster, not an
OL,8,Fadjudicator, and allegations of this
OL,9,Ftype are investigated by other bodies,
OL,10,Fincluding when complaints are raised
OL,11,Fby the police. What I can do, and have
OL,12,Fdone, as you have heard, is to
OL,13,Fcommission an external review, which I
OL,14,Fdid just days after being first
OL,15,Fcontacted by the BBC back in April."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
