OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FChannel 4's chief content officer, Ian
OL,8,FKatz, said Married At First Sight UK
OL,9,Fparticipants "were kept safe when any
OL,10,Fissues were raised" and were given
OL,11,F"appropriate support" after
OL,12,Fallegations of rape and sexual
OL,13,Fmisconduct were made.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
