OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FShona Manderson, the only woman of the
OL,8,Fthree who is identified, accused her
OL,9,Fon-screen partner of sexual misconduct
OL,10,Fwhile on the Channel 4 show. Her on-
OL,11,Fscreen partner, Bradley Skelly, told
OL,12,FPanorama he categorically denies "any
OL,13,Fallegations of sexual misconduct, or
OL,14,Fthat he was controlling".
OL,16,FDomestic abuse charity Women's Aid
OL,17,Fsaid the allegations made for
OL,18,F"disturbing and sobering" viewing.
OL,26,@tD@bOUvD@XO]zD@AOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
