OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FEarlier, MPs on the Culture, Media and
OL,13,FSport (CMS) Committee wrote to Channel
OL,14,F4 and Ofcom about their response to
OL,15,Fthe allegations, asking the
OL,16,Fbroadcaster about its complaints
OL,17,Fprocess for contestants on the
OL,18,Fprogramme and the steps taken to
OL,19,Fensure the allegations were fully
OL,20,Finvestigated, along with the review
OL,21,Fannounced by the broadcaster.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
