OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FOn Tuesday, police urged potential
OL,8,Fvictims of sexual assault on the
OL,9,Freality TV show to come forward. The
OL,10,Fshow, which is produced for Channel 4
OL,11,Fby independent production company CPL,
OL,12,Finvolves single people matched by
OL,13,Fexperts and then "marry", with couples
OL,14,Fmeeting for the first time on their
OL,15,Fwedding day.
OL,26,@uD@ROUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FChannel 4 said in a statement released
OL,8,Fon Monday: "In April, Channel 4 was
OL,9,Fpresented with serious allegations of
OL,10,Fwrongdoing against a small number of
OL,11,Fpast contributors, allegations that we
OL,12,Funderstand those contributors have
OL,13,Fdenied."
OL,15,FLawyers for CPL, the independent
OL,16,Fproduction company that produces the
OL,17,Fshow, told the BBC its welfare system
OL,18,Ffor MAFS is the "gold standard" and
OL,19,Findustry-leading. They said they acted
OL,20,Fappropriately in all of the cases
OL,21,Fraised by the BBC.
OL,26,@pD@LOUuD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
