OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FThe "marriages" on the show are not
OL,8,Flegally binding but the couples go on
OL,9,Fa "honeymoon" and move in together
OL,10,Fafter their weddings.
OL,12,FOne woman alleged to Panorama that her
OL,13,Fonscreen husband raped her and
OL,14,Fthreatened her with an acid attack
OL,16,FA second said she told both Channel 4
OL,17,Fand CPL about being allegedly raped by
OL,18,Fher on-screen husband, but that her
OL,19,Fepisodes were still aired.
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@OO]qD@COUqD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FChannel 4 has removed all previous
OL,8,Fseasons of the show from its streaming
OL,9,Fplatforms. Shortly before the Panorama
OL,10,Fepisode aired, Channel 4 announced it
OL,11,Fhad commissioned an external review
OL,12,Finto contributor welfare last month,
OL,13,Fwhich it expects to report in the
OL,14,Fcoming months.
OL,16,FSir Ian Cheshire, the government's
OL,17,Fcandidate to be the next Ofcom
OL,18,Fchairman, said he "welcomed" Channel
OL,19,F4's decision to investigate the
OL,20,Fallegations of rape on the show.
OL,26,@zD@SOUzD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779293476
OL,3,CChannel 4 boss 'deeply sorry' after
OL,4,CMarried At First Sight UK rape
OL,5,Callegations
OL,7,FSpeaking to the Science, Innovation
OL,8,Fand Technology Committee on Wednesday,
OL,9,FSir Ian, who was Channel 4's chairman
OL,10,Fbetween 2022 and 2025, said: "I
OL,11,Fwelcome the fact that Channel 4 are
OL,12,Ftaking the allegations seriously on
OL,13,FMarried At First Sight."
OL,15,FIt is understood that no decision has
OL,16,Fbeen made on future series of Married
OL,17,FAt First Sight.
OL,26,@rD@^OUuD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
